{"tid":1976982,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"其實要開始稱呼港共為「僞特區政府」","createTime":"2020-04-17T15:13:49.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-17T15:32:27.000Z","uid":128430,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e0a1da66e21c675e4f447513c735a9e7d6fc04fe","tid":1976982,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T15:13:49.000Z","msg":"如果港澳辦與中聯辦不受《基本法》第22條規管，言下之意，佢哋作出干預都是合法。<br />\n<br />\n如果中聯辦有監督權，而且無遠弗屆，事無不統，咁中聯辦就唔係聯絡辦公室，而係治港政權機關，特首唔係共匪語言講嘅「一把手」，中聯辦主任先係。特首要接受佢要監督<br />\n<br />\n若然如此，特區政府只係傀儡，同滿州國當年有個日本總務廳一樣。<br />\n<br />\n我哋應該開始稱呼政府做<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">僞特區政府</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c1c9e00d7b3508dc10253e6af3842b7d18b54f8","tid":1976982,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T15:14:33.000Z","msg":"港大法律學院首席講師張達明表示，中聯辦的聲明令他感到憂慮，似乎要顯示他們有權干預香港一切事務，若港澳辦與中聯辦不受《基本法》第22條規管，言下之意，他們不單可以「出聲」、甚至作出干預都是合法，這會是對一國兩制很新的解讀。"},{"pid":"597ffaa7e6725217e5ed11d900ee829c5ed2d00f","tid":1976982,"uid":177213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T15:15:01.000Z","msg":"Push！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n⚠️<span style=\"color: red;\">請注意以下專搶新Po頭幾則留言，再屈樓主係五毛嘅新五毛會員</span>&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">「好野可以出街lu」</span><br />\n<br />\n罪證<br />\n1. 胡亂屈樓主五毛<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/foJDuT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/foJDuT</a><br />\n#2 回覆 <br />\n<br />\n2.胡亂屈樓主五毛<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/foyAsT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/foyAsT</a><br />\n#4 回覆 <br />\n<br />\n3.明顯五毛言論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/foJCJT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/foJCJT</a><br />\n#4 回覆 <br />\n<br />\n4.明顯五毛言論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/foJPdT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/foJPdT</a><br />\n#8 回覆 <br />\n<br />\n5.承認自己係五毛<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/avuHgeV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/avuHgeV</a><br />\n#19 回覆"},{"pid":"ac2fbc1caf777425d68e17d52d87a188e4f2920b","tid":1976982,"uid":128430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T15:15:46.000Z","msg":"陳文敏認為，中聯辦的說法若屬實，將對香港很「危險」，因為代表港澳辦和中聯辦可以凌駕特區政府、介入及接管香港。他表示，中聯辦只是香港與中央之間的聯絡機構，而非管治機構，指中聯辦的說法越權、行使解釋基本法的權力"},{"pid":"308e64920eba32bdd2e8ba721df39834fd1481d5","tid":1976982,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T15:19:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"781185c52e93dc42489f4773d5fa08ccce75cf0e","tid":1976982,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T15:20:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3e402bea41cb160f565b8f296600088a852bfe21","tid":1976982,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T15:20:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9a17a088b128cde140752e964a4f978351613db6","tid":1976982,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T15:21:11.000Z","msg":"偽政府"},{"pid":"93ef6f6f658a1bea9f603ef77a6485c10cf4eaf7","tid":1976982,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T15:21:36.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"667d8e29c1ce7cc151b16ab9c863addedcbd1417","tid":1976982,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T15:21:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"af16d0a518e90f85995d1fae821afd09cace1a96","tid":1976982,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T15:22:01.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6e69a594a12b8ba793ba2cd7cd0b8acbcc014357","tid":1976982,"uid":128430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T15:22:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"92bf5c